    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(center)">Office of <persName>ALLEN &amp; CO.</persName>,</p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><placeName>6 BROAD STEET</placeName>,</p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>Decr. 18 1867</date></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir and friend</p>
            <p>Please send per express to<lb/>
                <persName>J. E. P. Lazarus</persName>
                <placeName>24 West 39th St</placeName>,<lb/> 1 <sic>sett</sic> prayer books for
                which I<lb/> enclose check $25.50 for the Books<lb/> and freight. I have not
                been<lb/> able to see any friend as yet in<lb/> regard to the Books.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Hoping you are feeling better</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I am yours very truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">M. M. Allen</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <placeName>P.O. Box 2380</placeName>
            </p>
            <p><persName>Rev. I. I. Lyon</persName> says he can sell some<lb/> of your Books and
                wants 20% discount<lb/> same as other agents. Do you agree?<lb/>
                <persName role="author">M.</persName></p>
        </body>
